  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "chapterTitle": "不成问题的问题",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "860438_3_3564-3979",
          "range": "3564-3979",
          "rangeStart": 3564,
          "rangeEnd": 3979,
          "markText": "四十来岁，中等身量，脸上有点发胖，而肉都是亮的，丁务源不是个俊秀的人，而令人喜爱。他脸上那点发亮的肌肉，已经教人一见就痛快，再加上一对光满神足、顾盼多姿的眼睛，与随时变化而无往不宜的表情，就不只讨人爱，而且令人信任他了。最足以表现他的天才而使人赞叹不已的是他的衣服。他的长袍，不管是绸的还是布的，不管是单的还是棉的，永远是半新半旧的，使人一看就感到舒服；永远是比他的身材稍微宽大一些，于是他垂着手也好，揣着手也好，掉背着手更好，老有一些从容不迫的气度。他的小褂的领子与袖口，永远是洁白如雪；这样，即使大褂上有一小块油渍，或大襟上微微有点褶皱，可是他的雪白的内衣的领与袖会使人相信他是最爱清洁的人。他老穿礼服呢厚白底子的鞋，而且裤脚儿上扎着绸子带儿；快走，那白白的鞋底与颤动的腿带，会显出轻灵飘洒；慢走，又显出雍容大雅。长袍、布底鞋、绸子裤脚带儿合在一处，未免太老派了，所以他在领子下面插上了一支派克笔和一支白亮的铅笔，来调和一下。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1654511064,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2022-06-06 18:24:24",
          "chapterUid": 3,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=860438&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3564&rangeEnd=3979",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/353328505d21163530129f5?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3564&rangeEnd=3979"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "860438_3_29222-29315",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "29222-29315",
      "markText": "到了夏天，葡萄与各种果树全比上年多结了三倍的果实，仿佛只有它们还记得尤大兴的培植与爱护似的。 果子结得越多，农场也不知怎么越赔钱。",
      "totalCount": 799,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=860438&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=29222&rangeEnd=29315",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/353328505d21163530129f5?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=29222&rangeEnd=29315"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "860438_3_4335-4355",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "4335-4355",
      "markText": "天下事都绝对没有问题，因为他根本不去办。",
      "totalCount": 490,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=860438&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=4335&rangeEnd=4355",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/353328505d21163530129f5?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=4335&rangeEnd=4355"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "860438_3_24665-24719",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "24665-24719",
      "markText": "不过，向上的路是极难走的。理智的崇高的决定，往往被一点点浮浅的，低卑的感情所破坏。情感是极容易发酒疯的东西。",
      "totalCount": 403,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=860438&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=24665&rangeEnd=24719",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/353328505d21163530129f5?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=24665&rangeEnd=24719"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "860438_3_4727-4770",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "4727-4770",
      "markText": "新主任到职以后，什么也没过问，而在两天之中把大家的姓名记得飞熟，并且知道了他们的籍贯。",
      "totalCount": 384,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=860438&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=4727&rangeEnd=4770",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/353328505d21163530129f5?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=4727&rangeEnd=4770"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "860438_38_1138-1158",
      "chapterUid": 38,
      "range": "1138-1158",
      "markText": "世界就是狼吞虎咽的世界，谁坏谁就占便宜。",
      "totalCount": 272,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=860438&chapterUid=38&rangeStart=1138&rangeEnd=1158",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/353328505d21163530129f5?chapterUid=38&rangeStart=1138&rangeEnd=1158"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "860438_3_22910-22929",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "22910-22929",
      "markText": "他们用按时间做事来遮掩他们的不会做事。",
      "totalCount": 256,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=860438&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=22910&rangeEnd=22929",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/353328505d21163530129f5?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=22910&rangeEnd=22929"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "860438_64_3716-3782",
      "chapterUid": 64,
      "range": "3716-3782",
      "markText": "我的眼前时常发黑，我仿佛已摸到了死，哼！我还笑，笑我这一辈的聪明本事，笑这出奇不公平的世界，希望等我笑到末一声，这世界就换个样儿吧！",
      "totalCount": 256,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=860438&chapterUid=64&rangeStart=3716&rangeEnd=3782",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/353328505d21163530129f5?chapterUid=64&rangeStart=3716&rangeEnd=3782"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "860438_3_25236-25320",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "25236-25320",
      "markText": "他甚至于想到，大家满可以毫无理由地打击他、驱逐他，可是他决不退缩、妥协。科学的方法与法律的生活，是建设新中国的必经的途径。假若他为这两件事而被打，好吧，他愿做了殉道者。",
      "totalCount": 240,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=860438&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=25236&rangeEnd=25320",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/353328505d21163530129f5?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=25236&rangeEnd=25320"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "860438_3_7279-7328",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "7279-7328",
      "markText": "有时候，黄鼠狼在白天就出来为非作歹，而在他们最猖獗的时间，连牛犊和羊羔都被劫去；多么大的黄鼠狼呀！",
      "totalCount": 238,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=860438&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=7279&rangeEnd=7328",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/353328505d21163530129f5?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=7279&rangeEnd=7328"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "860438_3_2129-2178",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "2129-2178",
      "markText": "农场赔钱？这伤了他的自尊心。他赔点钱，股东他们赔点钱，都没有关系：只是，下不来台！这比什么都要紧！",
      "totalCount": 234,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=860438&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2129&rangeEnd=2178",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/353328505d21163530129f5?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2129&rangeEnd=2178"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "860438_5_6757-6842",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "6757-6842",
      "markText": "夜静人稀，沙子龙关好了小门，一气把六十四枪刺下来；而后，拄着枪，望着天上的群星，想起当年在野店荒林的威风。叹一口气，用手指慢慢摸着凉滑的枪身，又微微一笑：“不传！不传！”",
      "totalCount": 198,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=860438&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=6757&rangeEnd=6842",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/353328505d21163530129f5?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=6757&rangeEnd=6842"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "860438_3_1661-1737",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1661-1737",
      "markText": "无论是内行人还是外行人，只要看过这座农场，大概就不会想象到这是赔钱的事业。 然而，树华农场赔钱。",
      "totalCount": 196,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=860438&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1661&rangeEnd=1737",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/353328505d21163530129f5?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1661&rangeEnd=1737"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "860438_3_523-548",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "523-548",
      "markText": "江水在冬天与春天总是使人愿意跳进去的那么澄清碧绿。",
      "totalCount": 192,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=860438&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=523&rangeEnd=548",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/353328505d21163530129f5?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=523&rangeEnd=548"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "860438_38_1307-1329",
      "chapterUid": 38,
      "range": "1307-1329",
      "markText": "钱比人更厉害一些，人若是兽，钱就是兽的胆子。",
      "totalCount": 182,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=860438&chapterUid=38&rangeStart=1307&rangeEnd=1329",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/353328505d21163530129f5?chapterUid=38&rangeStart=1307&rangeEnd=1329"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "860438_18_765-840",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "765-840",
      "markText": "在事后一想，我们娘儿俩就像两个没人管的狗，为我们的嘴，我们得受着一切的苦处，好像我们身上没有别的，只有一张嘴。为这张嘴，我们得把其余一切的东西都卖了。",
      "totalCount": 180,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=860438&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=765&rangeEnd=840",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/353328505d21163530129f5?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=765&rangeEnd=840"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "860438_3_11767-11816",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "11767-11816",
      "markText": "“秦妙斋，艺术家秦妙斋。你记住，艺术家和秦妙斋老得一块儿喊出来；一分开，艺术家和我就都不存在了！”",
      "totalCount": 176,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=860438&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=11767&rangeEnd=11816",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/353328505d21163530129f5?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=11767&rangeEnd=11816"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "860438_3_4560-4612",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "4560-4612",
      "markText": "于是一部分有经验的职员与工人马上被他“欢送”出去，而舅爷与舅爷的舅爷都成了护法的天使，占据了地上的乐园。",
      "totalCount": 170,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=860438&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=4560&rangeEnd=4612",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/353328505d21163530129f5?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=4560&rangeEnd=4612"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "860438_3_4008-4021",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "4008-4021",
      "markText": "他老在说话，而并没说什么。",
      "totalCount": 165,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=860438&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=4008&rangeEnd=4021",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/353328505d21163530129f5?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=4008&rangeEnd=4021"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "860438_3_5860-5946",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "5860-5946",
      "markText": "有时候，主妇们因为丁主任太好铺张而想表示不满，可是丁主任送来的礼物，与对她们的殷勤，使她们也无从开口。她们既不出声，男人们就感到事情都办得合理，而把丁主任看成了不起的人物。",
      "totalCount": 162,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=860438&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=5860&rangeEnd=5946",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/353328505d21163530129f5?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=5860&rangeEnd=5946"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "860438_38_936-949",
      "chapterUid": 38,
      "range": "936-949",
      "markText": "“教育”是有用的，我相信了",
      "totalCount": 162,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=860438&chapterUid=38&rangeStart=936&rangeEnd=949",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/353328505d21163530129f5?chapterUid=38&rangeStart=936&rangeEnd=949"
    }
  ],
